字段详细信息

compiled

public Hashtable compiled
A table mapping flat names of all compiled classes in this run to their symbols; maintained from outside.

deprecatedSource

public Name deprecatedSource
Output variable: the source file where deprecated symbols were encountered. If deprecated symbols were encountered in more than one input file, the variable is set to "*".

uncheckedSource

public Name uncheckedSource
Output variable: the source file where deprecated symbols were encountered. If deprecated symbols were encountered in more than one input file, the variable is set to "*".

firstIncompatibility

public Symbol firstIncompatibility(Type t1,
                                   Type t2,
                                   Type site)
Return the first method which is defined with same args but different return types in two given interfaces, or null if none exists.

参数：
t1 - The first interface.
t2 - The second interface.
site - The most derived type.

firstIncompatibility

public Symbol firstIncompatibility(Type t1,
                                   Type t2,
                                   Type t2super,
                                   Type site)
Return the first method which is defined with same args but different return types in a type `t1' and a supertype `t2super' of a type `t2', or null if none exists.

参数：
t1 - The first type.
t2 - The second type.
t2super - The second's supertype.
site - The most derived type.

checkCompatible

public boolean checkCompatible(int pos,
                               Type t1,
                               Type t2)
Check that (arrays of) interfaces do not each define a method with same name and arguments but different return types. If either argument type is not an (array of) interface type, do nothing.

参数：
pos - Position to be used for error reporting.
t1 - The first argument type.
t2 - The second argument type.

checkCompatibleAbstracts

public boolean checkCompatibleAbstracts(int pos,
                                        Type t1,
                                        Type t2,
                                        Type site)
Check that classes (or interfaces) do not each define an abstract method with same name and arguments but different return types.

参数：
pos - Position to be used for error reporting.
t1 - The first argument type.
t2 - The second argument type.

public void checkCanonical(Tree tree)
Check that a qualified name is in canonical form (for import decls).
